    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[1].lines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.size
      value: 3
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[3].lines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.size
      value: 3
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[5].lines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[6].lines.Array.size
      value: 3
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[7].lines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[8].lines.Array.size
      value: 4
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[9].lines.Array.size
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Sorry I just... I still can't believe it.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: You knew the suspect?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Since we were kids. We were close.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Our fathers were friends. Sunday lunches, town fiestas...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: It felt like one big family back then.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: When did things change between him and his father?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: I'm not sure. He just... drifted.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Stopped coming around. Stopped talking.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: When I'd ask he'd just say everything was fine.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[5].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Did he ever say anything about his father that worried you?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[6].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: There were small things. Little comments.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[6].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: I didn't think much of it then.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[6].lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: Now I replay every conversation wondering what I missed.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[7].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: And now he's gone.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[8].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Wherever he is...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[8].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: I hope he's found before he does something else.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[8].lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: But part of me also hopes he's okay.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[8].lines.Array.data[3]'
      value: Is that wrong of me?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[9].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: ...No.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7429431213665447145, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[9].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: It's not wrong at all.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    m_RemovedComponents: []
    m_RemovedGameObjects: []
    m_AddedGameObjects: []
    m_AddedComponents:
    - targetCorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 2018793025095296489, guid: 3243c520fcb651348b5d8185ebf0508b, type: 3}
